These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  social-worker, freelancer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, house
1. the freelancer is somewhere to the left of the fan of punk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Job           | freelancer | social-worker |
| Music-Genre   | house     | punk  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, dog
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, helicopter
1. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Pet         | dog   | hedgehog      |
| Transport   | snowmobile | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, folk
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, skateboard
1. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | folk | techno    |
| Transport     | helicopter | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
